{"tid":53652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大宣佈：高速寬頻上網是每個市民應有的基本服務","createTime":"2016-12-24T22:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T09:37:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2caa2021816b3fe47473c8b1f3afdcb606f5fbb3","tid":53652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T22:47:29.000Z","msg":"加拿大宣佈：高速寬頻上網是每個市民應有的基本服務<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://css.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/canada1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcss.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fcanada1.jpg&h=41d65a4e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然現時我們的生活都無可避免地圍繞互聯網，不過要得到穩定高速的上網服務，卻不是必然的事情。最近加拿大政府就宣佈，把得到高速上網服務定為市民的基本權利。 <br />\n<br />\n加拿大的電訊管理局 CRTC 早前在一個記者會上公佈，為了加拿大未來的經濟和社會發展，以及每個市民的未來，正式把高速寬頻上網服務，列爲「基本電訊服務」，也就是與家用電話服務擁有一樣的地位。為了實行這個標準，加拿大政府也準備投資 7.5 億美元，去為偏遠郊區鋪設上網基建，讓當地居民也可以擁有「基本」的高速上網服務。 <br />\n<br />\n而他們所謂高速的上網服務，也有個新的標準。有線的寬頻服務而言，所需要的下載速度最少應為 50 Mbps，上載則是 10 Mbps，相比 2011 年的目標提升了 10 倍，不過對於無線上網的目標就簡單得多，只要求可以得到最新的流動無線科技。他們估計現時大概 18% 的市民未得到上述的上網服務，將會補貼基建服務協助他們，，預期在 2021 年達到 90% 市民獲得的上網服務能達到這個標準。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2016/12/24/canada-broadband-internet-essential-service/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2Fcanada-broadband-internet-essential-service%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=NfLHfgbwHVIQMAjoJl73snvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=95050aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2016/12/24/canada-broadband-internet-essential-service/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"189a704eb8a95f32eff174db3ad152b81ebcf831","tid":53652,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T22:50:12.000Z","msg":"仲好過pccw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470a8c9d64101a21cc3cf6d2ab23de761460d1ed","tid":53652,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T23:01:42.000Z","msg":"加拿大郊區上網真係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n竟然有限data嘅家用上網<br />\n街冇鋪線又迫住用衛星，一多雲多雨多雪就上唔到，電視都睇唔到"},{"pid":"284db175ecffab1b84b4bae49116b6a79da3db2c","tid":53652,"uid":3052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T23:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲好過pccw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網快唔斷真係要謝李隆恩"},{"pid":"1240fde1b1b1b14fdf1fb206f9bbdb1f50ecd81d","tid":53652,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T00:18:58.000Z","msg":"pccw電話線上網 是 香港人基本服務"},{"pid":"7a6fb8479fcca36fc203ee6213315d4f14ecd667","tid":53652,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T00:29:49.000Z","msg":"56k已足夠"},{"pid":"238cf490e0cd1826b7b326a7362992ef4085b709","tid":53652,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T01:06:34.000Z","msg":"Pccw每日都斷幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b468600810b393e2a8acab9dfc07c4a44e6c092e","tid":53652,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"8m download 0.2m upload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b66c970798a1731dd51f5b8ede3531145e90332","tid":53652,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  村屋撚已習慣亀速"},{"pid":"eca51bb44abfd5aeba49d79c64b5a192770f47a3","tid":53652,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"香港村屋而家忍緊咩速度"},{"pid":"31b4d4b93e72accb0f918d51a6a377da92a7949e","tid":53652,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加拿大郊區上網真係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n竟然有限data嘅家用上網<br />\n街冇鋪線又迫住用衛星，一多雲多雨多雪就上唔到，電視都睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人少需求低就係咁"},{"pid":"b9ac87234